title: Metal Gear Solid V: The Phantom Pain - Update 2 (Not Cracked)
description:
Important note: I will be uploading updates as best I can. So when the crack does come out, all that will be required is to copy the crack over and play.

Install instructions:
Note: Most likely requires Update 1 installed
1. Download
2. Copy contents to main game directory and overwrite
3. Wait for crack 

Changelist:
Beta 1.003 has been released.
- Fixed an issue where the settings in the "OPTIONS" > "KEY ASSIGNMENT" menu would revert to the default values when restarting the game.
- Fixed various issues that were resulting in a black or white screen on startup, such as when using a resolution below 1280x720
